You can use [flutter_form_bloc](https://github.com/GiancarloCode/form_bloc/tree/master/packages/flutter_form_bloc), you don&#39;t need to create any `TextEditingController` and can separate the Business Logic from the User Interface, in addition to offering other advantages.

```yaml
dependencies:
